<li>7/26/95 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/govern/em422.html">Truth In Testimony: Uncovering the <i>Real</i> Special Interests</a> by <a href="/heritage/staff/wittmann.htm">Marshall Wittmann</a> and Charles P. Griffin. (Executive Memorandum #422) 
