<HEAD>
<title>Taxpayer Protection Pledge</title>
</HEAD>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<CENTER><H2>The Pledge Takers for the 104th Congress</H2>
<HR>
<H3>As of Thursday, September 19, 1996</H3></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER>By State</CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><small>
