<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/pff/clean/exec.html 204.71.237.86 19970108151443 text/html 10517
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 15:14:52 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jul-96 19:36:40 GMT
