//www.senate.gov/~burns/crypto.htm"><b>encryption.</b></a><br>
<img src="/pff/diamond.gif" hspace="5" vspace="4" align="top"><a href="/pff/cad/spec396.html"><b>The Property Status of Airwaves</b></a> by Ayn Rand<br>
