<DOCNO>WT16-B20-120</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000256-B009-141</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/pff/i-cpr.html 204.71.237.86 19970108151743 text/html 5643
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
