http://www.sbsc.org:80/conservative/hotissues/dale.html 204.71.237.86 19970108064226 text/html 2873
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 06:42:43 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 11-Sep-96 18:41:00 GMT
Content-length: 2684
